Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.12,0:21:35.34,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}遗失了开启乐园的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.18,0:21:40.18,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}接受惩罚死去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.82,0:21:44.46,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}向着深夜的迷途
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.40,0:21:49.50,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}无法忍受的荆棘
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.02,0:21:53.45,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}松开的锁链
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.62,0:22:03.14,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}追寻着永远被埋葬的爱
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.91,0:22:12.73,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}请不要看这残破的我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.09,0:22:21.92,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}破裂的牵绊 黑色的安魂曲
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.31,0:22:31.18,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}请不要来这里 这你未知的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.57,0:22:38.50,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}下着绝望的雨的世界……
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.55,0:22:39.95,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}现在、完结
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.13,0:22:45.60,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}如火焰般闪耀于汝等心中
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.03,0:22:47.86,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}主宰汝等…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.12,0:21:35.34,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}楽園の扉開く　鍵を　失くして
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.18,0:21:40.18,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}罰を受けし心は
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.82,0:21:44.46,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}夜の迷路へ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.40,0:21:49.50,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}茨の王　赦さず
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.02,0:21:53.45,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}解けめ鎖
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.62,0:22:03.14,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}求めたのは　永遠　埋めたは愛
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.91,0:22:12.73,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}穢れ壊れた　僕をみないで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.09,0:22:21.92,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}裂かれた絆　黒きレクイエム
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.31,0:22:31.18,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}ここにこないで　君は知らないで
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.57,0:22:38.50,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}絶望の雨が降れる　世界が……
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.55,0:22:39.95,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}今、終わる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.13,0:22:45.60,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}Which Shinetu as a flame in the midst of your palace
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.03,0:22:47.86,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,200)\blur2}And reigneth Amongst…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.22,0:00:59.20,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}月亮在轻轻低语
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.87,0:01:04.23,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}以谁也听不到的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.21,0:01:08.58,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}不断满涨的潮水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.65,0:01:12.54,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}消失渐远的记忆中的情景
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.98,0:01:18.22,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}星星在密密记述着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.59,0:01:22.99,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}以谁也无法解读的文字
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.45,0:01:28.05,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}无限的语言的涡旋中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.36,0:01:32.70,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}千亿本书由此诞生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.70,0:01:40.27,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}我的天空无限广阔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.69,0:01:45.09,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}时间在飞速的镌刻
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.22,0:01:50.75,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}毫无所知的虚无
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.16,0:01:54.21,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}汇聚的语言
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.08,0:01:58.14,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}也只能在泥土中枯朽
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.99,0:02:04.98,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}即使如此我仍在呼唤
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.25,0:02:10.08,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}扬起晦涩难懂的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.48,0:02:15.26,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}至少将这声音传至天际
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.07,0:02:20.79,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,250)\blur3}太阳也终会升起吧
